column1: Expenditures per Pupil for Elementary and Secondary Public Schools, by state: 1993–2016

NOTES: The national total for public school expenditures for the United States includes U.S. territories. Please see source for information on estimation methodology. The national enrollment total for the United States includes U.S. territories.
